{"_path":"/trail/t010","_dir":"trail","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"森林步道","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":10,"category":"林口","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-30T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"森林步道"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"森林步道"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"步道簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"步道簡介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林口森林步道，遠離塵囂，人煙雜沓的地方，位於新北市林口區頂福里頂福巖顯應祖師廟左後方的山邊，林口頂福巖顯應祖師廟主要祀奉顯應祖師，於民國 83 年 9 月 27 日入廟安座，是早年泉州安溪人的信仰。步道入口設有導覽地圖，地圖後方為愛心杖及愛心傘放置區域供登山遊客使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林口森林步道為溪流山澗切割分散的丘陵谷地，海拔約 200~250 公尺的丘陵地，全程有 4,270 公尺。步道之完成，得力於林口登山健行協會用心開闢整理出來的一條原始森林步道，協會義工所用近自然工法，使步道儘量融入自然環境與地景之中，除必要之休憩及安全設施外，少用過多的人工構造物，且步道保持自然土路路面，沿途尚可見多種中低海拔次森林之樹種，讓人體驗走在這蒼翠綠意盎然的原始森林裡。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"自行開車"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自行開車"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由文化北路--遇中山路左轉產業道路--前行 2 公里到達林口頂福巖顯應祖師廟左後方，即可見到林口頂福巖森林步道入口。經產業道路至目的地都是雙向道路。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"停車：在頂福巖顯應祖師廟周圍都有停車位"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公共運輸"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公共運輸"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"沒有便捷的公共交通到達此處，建議開車前往。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"相關介紹"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相關介紹"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健行筆記 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://hiking.biji.co/index.php?q=news&act=info&id=11663"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林口森林步道"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Youtube 2021/07/25 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-AtllrghFhg"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"連林口人也不一定來過的地方！上集"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t010-01.jpeg","src":"/images/trail/t010-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"森林步道","depth":2,"text":"森林步道","children":[{"id":"步道簡介","depth":3,"text":"步道簡介"},{"id":"自行開車","depth":3,"text":"自行開車"},{"id":"公共運輸","depth":3,"text":"公共運輸"},{"id":"相關介紹","depth":3,"text":"相關介紹"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:trail:t010.md","_source":"content","_file":"trail/t010.md","_extension":"md"}